article.headline: Loyola Marymount wins 67-47 against UTEP
article.description: — Justin Wright had 20 points in Loyola Marymount's 67-47 win against UTEP on Saturday night.
article.story: LOS ANGELES -- — Justin Wright had 20 points in Loyola Marymount's 67-47 win against UTEP on Saturday night. Wright added six rebounds for the Lions (4-3). Keli Leaupepe and Lars Thiemann added 13 points apiece. The Miners (5-2) were led by Tae Hardy, who recorded 12 points. Zid Powell added nine points and six rebounds for UTEP. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
